c-label%3D%5C%22What%20makes%20this%20dog%20snuffle%20mat%20stand%20out%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20makes%20this%20dog%20snuffle%20mat%20stand%20out%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPaw5's%20emphasis%20on%20sustainability%20places%20the%20Wooly%20Snuffle%20Mat%20above%20the%20competition.%20Each%20mat%20is%20handmade%20from%20upcycled%20polyester%20and%20cotton%20fabric%20that%20is%20soft%20and%20non%20abrasive%20on%20a%20dog's%20nose.%20It's%20also%20easy%20to%20clean.%20After%20a%20few%20uses%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20throw%20it%20in%20the%20wash.%20Even%20after%20more%20than%2020%20washes%2C%20our%20mat%20still%20looks%20good.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22713a9919-1241-4854-ad77-0037caa41d4e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20cons%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20cons%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mat%20can%20hold%20the%20odors%20of%20the%20treats%20and%20tempt%20some%20dogs%20to%20chew%20it%2C%20so%20you%20should%20supervise%20your%20pet.%20Also%2C%20the%20mat%20doesn't%20have%20a%20no-slip%20bottom%2C%20so%20I've%20found%20it%20works%20best%20on%20carpet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20a%20game%20for%20all%20your%20dogs%20to%20play%20together.%20I%20put%20one%20of%20our%20dogs%20behind%20a%20baby%20gate%20so%20they%20each%20have%20their%20own%20turn%20at%20the%20game.%20You%20don't%20want%20to%20encourage%20guarding%20behavior.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221b4396f4-49a6-45f3-8684-d0b5b645533d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20bottom%20line%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20very%20few%20products%20I've%20found%20that%20burn%20energy%20indoors%20and%20tire%20out%20my%20two%20hounds.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-40651-20%26h%3D5f776e13dbf5d38f361fc54321b5a5a162c95c147ead70bbf224eb6b216afb9a%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42c41%26postSlug%3Dguides%25