Set%20up%20an%20area%20to%20clean%20your%20dog's%20ears%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Ear%20cleaning%20can%20be%20messy.%20You%20can%20use%20a%20towel%20and%20set%20up%20in%20your%20bathroom%20or%20even%20outdoors.%20I%20find%20cleaning%20outside%20is%20easiest%20as%20natural%20light%20helps%20when%20you're%20trying%20to%20clean%20the%20smaller%20areas%20of%20the%20ear%20flap.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EUnderstand%20the%20anatomy%20of%20your%20dog's%20ear%20canal%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22dog%20ear%20diagram%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5eab446d14419225206d3596%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3Ealexandragl1%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20understand%20that%20you're%20%3Cem%3Eonly%3C%2Fem%3E%20cleaning%20the%20outer%20ear.%C2%A0The%20ear%20has%20three%20major%20parts%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOuter%20ear%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20outer%20ear%20includes%20the%20ear%20flap%2C%20which%20may%20be%20floppy%20like%20that%20of%20a%20hound%2C%20stiff%20and%20pointy%20like%20that%20of%20a%20shepherd%2C%20or%20somewhere%20in%20between.%20Then%20there's%20the%20outer%20ear%20canal%2C%20which%20is%20long%20and%20narrow%20and%20bends%20at%20an%20almost-90-degree%20angle%20before%20the%20eardrum%20(tympanic%20membrane)%20and%20middle%20ear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMiddle%20ear%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20eardrum%20separates%20the%20outer%20and%20middle%20parts%20of%20the%20ear.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20avoid%20the%20eardrum%20during%20cleaning%20as%20it%20can%20be%20easily%20damaged.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInner%20ear%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20is%20the%20innermost%20part%20of%20the%20ear%20where%20the%20cochlea%2C%20nerves%2C%20and%20balance%20mechanisms%20are%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20to%20apply%20the%20ear%20cleaning%20solution%3Cfigure%3E%3C