20give%20it%20a%20try%20myself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20dog%20mom%20to%20a%20miniature%20Australian%20shepherd%20named%20Walker%2C%20I'm%20no%20stranger%20to%20dog%20hair.%20It's%20everywhere%2C%20all%20the%20time.%20But%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-pet-vacuum%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epull%20out%20the%20vacuum%3C%2Fa%3E%20every%20day.%20(I%20can%20be%20lazy.)%20So%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20see%20if%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-56409-20%26h%3D054bdb46bdb7550dd41c3c6c8a2a7240696bf5f7c04559feaecda6cc097820ae%26postID%3D6310ecb59305540b6b372e2e%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fchomchom-roller-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FPet-Dog-Cat-Hair-Remover-Couch%252Fdp%252FB00BAGTNAQ%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChomChom%20Roller%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20be%20the%20solution%20to%20my%20daily%20dog%20hair%20debacle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20review%20of%20the%20ChomChom%20Roller%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20is%20a%20ChomChom%20Roller%3F%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221704%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20holds%20a%20ChomChom%20Roller%20above%20a%20couch%2C%20and%20the%20device%20has%20a%20few%20hairs%20stuck%20to%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6310ef123fe7c40019e4e301%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBrenna%20Darling%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EClaiming%20to%20be%20the%20%26quot%3Bworld's%20best%20pet%20hair%20remover%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-56409-20%26h%3D054bdb46bdb7550dd41c3c6c8a2a7240696bf5f7c04559feaecda6cc097820ae%26postID%3D6310ecb59305540b6b372e2e%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fchomchom-roller-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FPet-Dog-Cat-Hair-Remover-Couch%252Fdp%252FB00BAGTNAQ%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChomChom%20Roller%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20reusable%2C%20eco-friendly%2C%20and%20really%20easy%20to%20use.%20The%20fur%20remover%20is%20made%20mostly%20of%20nylon%20in%20a%20plastic%20case%20and%20works%20on%20just%20about%20anything%20made%20of%20fabric%2C%20including%20sofas%2C%20rugs%2C%20bedspreads%2C%20and%20clothing.%20No%20batteries%20or%20power%20source%20is%20required%2C%20and%20the%20only%20maintenance%20needed%20is%20occasionally%20cleaning%20the%20brush%20surface%20with%20a%20water-soaked%20towel.%20ChomChom%20recommends%20not%20using%20the%20roller%20on%20wood%20flooring%2C%20tile%2C%20or%20concrete%20or%20on%20wet%20surfaces.%20Also%2C%20do%20not%20use%20it%20directly%20on%20your%20pets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20used%20the%20ChomChom%20all%20over%20my%20house%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20image%20of%20a%20brown%20pillow%20on%20a%20plaid%20sheet%2C%20one%20before%20using%20the%20ChomChom%20Roller%20and%20covered%20in%20fur%20and%20the%20other%20after%20with%20no%20fur%20visible.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6310ef873fe7c40019e4e330%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBrenna%20Darling%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20can%20be%20summed%20up%20in%20one%20word%3A%20easy.%20Starting%20with%20my%20living%20room%20area%20rug%2C%20I%20held%20the%20handle%20of%20the%20roller%20and%20pushed%20it%20backward%20and%20forward.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FH5WwDAECcrU%3Ft%3D85%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow-to%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20device's%20creator%20explains%20that%20the%20roller%20works%20best%20with%20a%20vigorous%20back-and-forth%20movement.%20It%20still%20picks%20up%20hair%20with%20a%20slower%20motion%2C%20so%20you%20can%20use%20it%20gently%20if%20you're%20worried%20about%20more%20delicate%20fabric.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20tested%20it%20out%20on%20a%20gray%20upholstered%20sectional%2C%20my%20silky%20green%20duvet%20cover%2C%20and%20my%20black%20leggings.%20It%20was%20shocking%20to%20see%20how%20much%20dog%20fur%20came%20up.%20In%20total%2C%20each%20area%20took%20less%20than%20three%20minutes%20to%20clean.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20ChomChom%20did%20de-fur%20my%20leggings%20while%20I%20was%20wearing%20them%2C%20it%20probably%20won't%20replace%20a%20lint%20roller%20for%20your%20clothes.%20It%20works%20best%20on%20fabric%20that%20won't%20bunch%20up%20while%20you're%20rolling%20over%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20fur-collection%20compartment%20makes%20this%20roller%20easy%20to%20clean%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221704%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20removes%20a%20large%20clump%20of%20dog%20fur%20from%20the%20back%20compartment%20of%20a%20ChomChom%20Roller.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6310f0183fe7c40019e4e344%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBrenna%20Darling%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nice%20thing%20about%20the%20ChomChom%20is%20that%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20remove%20the%20fur%20from%20the%20nylon%20roller%20itself.%20As%20you%20push%20the%20remover%20forward%20and%20backward%2C%20it%20doesn't%20fully%20rotate%20like%20a%20lint%20roller.%20Instead%2C%20plastic%20fins%20stop%20its%20movement%20so%20the%20fur%20is%20scraped%20off%20into%20a%20compartment%20in%20the%20back%20of%20the%20device.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20finishing%20an%20area%2C%20I%20clicked%20open%20the%20compartment's%20lid%20with%20the%20button%20and%20emptied%20Walker's%20hair%20into%20a%20trash%20can.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20fur%20in%20there%2C%20so%20I%20did%20have%20to%20use%20my%20fingers%20to%20get%20it%20all%20out.%20Afterward%2C%20I%20closed%20the%20lid%20and%20reused%20it%20until%20I%20couldn't%20see%20any%20more%20hair.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20ChomChom%20is%20now%20part%20of%20my%20daily%20routine%20(and%20much%20quicker%20than%20pulling%20out%20a%20vacuum)%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221704%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%E2%80%99s%20legs%20wearing%20black%20leggings%2C%20with%20one%20leg%20covered%20in%20pet%20hair%20and%20the%20other%20free%20of%20pet%20hair%2C%20next%20to%20a%20ChomChom%20Roller.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6310f0533fe7c40019e4e35b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBrenna%20Darling%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can%20confidently%20say%20this%20is%20the%20best%20pet-hair%20remover%20I've%20ever%20used.%20It's%20extremely%20easy%20and%20convenient%20to%20roll%20over%20my%20duvet%20cover%20every%20morning%20(because%2C%20admittedly%2C%20I%20let%20Walker%20snuggle%20in%20the%20bed)%2C%20so%20I've%20been%20able%20to%20incorporate%20it%20into%20my%20routine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20much%20prefer%20it%20for%20day-to-day%20use%20over%20the%20vacuum%2C%20and%20before%20guests%20come%20over%2C%20I%20quickly%20can%20clean%20fur%20from%20the%20sofa.%20Also%2C%20it's%20not%20sticky%20like%20a%20typical%20lint%20roller%2C%20and%20there%20are%20no%20sheets%20you%20need%20to%20throw%20away%20or%20refill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20are%20the%20cons%3F%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20small%2C%20handheld%20device%2C%20so%20I%20wouldn't%20recommend%20the%20ChomChom%20for%20a%20larger%20area.%20I%20guess%20the%20vacuum%20has%20to%20come%20out%20sometimes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20also%20have%20to%20get%20your%20hands%20a%20little%20dirty%20emptying%20the%20back%20compartment.%20Even%20knocking%20the%20roller%20against%20a%20trash%20can%20doesn't%20always%20fully%20dislodge%20the%20fur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221704%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20happy-looking%20dog%20sits%20on%20a%20color%20rug%20near%20a%20ChomChom%20Roller%20in%20a%20living%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6310f0973fe7c40019e4e37e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBrenna%20Darling%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ChomChom%20Roller%20is%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20gadgets%2C%20and%20I'd%20recommend%20it%20to%20anyone%20with%20a%20pet.%20It's%20inexpensive%2C%20endlessly%20reusable%2C%20and%20a%20great%20way%20to%20keep%20a%20dog-%20or%20cat-hair-free%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWorks%20very%20well%2C%20reusable%2C%20easy%20to%20use%2C%20no%20sticky%20tape%2C%20quick%20results%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENot%20ideal%20for%20large%20areas%2C%20you%20have%20to%20use%20your%20fingers%20to%20clean%20out%20the%20fur%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fchomchom-roller-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777212479000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6310ee583e08f700196c6088%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fchomchom-roller-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20trying%20a%20friend's%20ChomChom%20Roller%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20needed%20one%20of%20my%20own.%20I%20use%20it%20to%20remove%20dog%20fur%20throughout%20my%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Brenna%20Darling)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22