%3Cem%3EZachary%20Biss%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%2029%2C%20a%20musician%20from%20St.%20Petersburg%2C%20Florida%2C%20who%20moved%20with%20his%20girlfriend%2C%20Marina%2C%20to%20Portugal%20by%20boat.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20full-time%20musician.%20Back%20in%20the%20States%2C%20I%20played%20gigs%20at%20bars%20and%20restaurants%20with%20my%20guitar%2C%20singing%20and%20playing%20covers%20for%20a%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20had%20the%20same%20job%20in%20music%2C%20and%20over%20time%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20play%20all%20my%20gigs%20and%20have%20enough%20money%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20month%20to%20put%20away%20in%20savings%20and%20invest%20in%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20allowed%20me%20to%20buy%20a%20house%20in%20Florida%20in%202019.%20I%20was%20really%20proud%20that%20I%20was%20able%20to%20make%20that%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20I%20moved%20into%20the%20house%2C%20I've%20kept%20a%20budget%20down%20to%20the%20penny%2C%20and%20the%20expenses%20got%20absolutely%20insane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-bills-surge-utilities-31b-rate-increases-2025-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMy%20electric%20bill%20roughly%20doubled%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20course%20of%20five%20years.%20My%20utilities%2C%20which%20covered%20water%20and%20garbage%20disposal%2C%20doubled%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20all%20these%20people%20telling%20you%20homeownership%20is%20the%20goal%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20the%20dream%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20bills%20kept%20going%20up.%20I'm%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20seems%20backward.%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20should%20be%20paying%20something%20off%20to%20where%20eventually%20I'll%20be%20paying%20less.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20course%20of%20half%20a%20decade%2C%20everything%20has%20crept%20up%20to%20where%20I'm%20working%20harder%20than%20I've%20ever%20worked%2C%20and%20making%20as%20much%20money%20as%20I've%20ever%20made%2C%20but%20I%20have%20nothing%20to%20show%20for%20it%20here.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f0bb0154-c6a4-44a2-a9b5-0182df0456e7%5C%22%3EWe%20knew%20we%20wanted%20to%20move%20to%20Lisbon%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%2C%20maybe%20it's%20time%20to%20go%20somewhere%20else%20and%20try%20something%20different%2C%20because%20otherwise%20I'm%20just%20going%20to%20float%20here%20and%20not%20really%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20and%20woman%20drinking%20beer.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e9262aa98bc8fdc096d97b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBiss%20and%20his%20girlfriend%2C%20Marina.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Zachary%20Biss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20haven't%20sold%20my%20home%20yet.%20It's%20still%20on%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20girlfriend%20and%20I%20already%20knew%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-portugal-left-after-years-downsides-struggles-home-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewanted%20to%20move%20to%20Portugal%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20while.%20So%20by%20the%20time%20we%20were%20able%20to%20finally%20move%2C%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20care.%20We%20just%20have%20to%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20little%20bit%20emotional%2C%20but%20not%20really%20because%20we'd%20been%20planning%20it%20for%20so%20long.%20I%20had%20gotten%20to%20the%20point%20where%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20wait%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c69d781a-8988-4bc3-9c31-19cccf5fc422%5C%22%3EWe%20decided%20to%20move%20by%20taking%20a%20cruise%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20found%20a%20cruise%20that%20was%20actually%20going%20directly%20one%20way%2C%20because%20they%20do%20the%20transatlantic%20sailings%20to%20move%20the%20boats.%20After%20the%20season's%20over%20in%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feuropean-international-cruise-mistakes-from-first-timer-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emove%20to%20Europe%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20we%20found%20one%20that%20was%20going%20from%20Tampa%20and%20ending%20in%20Lisbon.%20It%20was%20a%20match%20made%20in%20heaven.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20did%20pay%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20than%20flying%2C%20but%20you're%20getting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falaska-cruise-with-extended-family-planning-pros-cons-multigenerational-vacation-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20two-week%20cruise%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20all%20the%20food%2C%20all%20the%20lodging%2C%20and%20a%20couple%20of%20stops%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-rented-private-boat-for-vacation-reasons-not-worth-it-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWe%20stopped%20in%20the%20Bahamas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20then%20after%20the%20Bahamas%20were%20six%20days%20at%20sea%2C%20and%20that%20was%20pretty%20wild.%20I've%20never%20spent%20that%20much%20time%20at%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fincredible-azores-islands-2015-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20Azores%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20then%20it%20was%20another%20sea%20day%20because%20they're%20pretty%20far%20off%20from%20the%20mainland.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fissues-living-in-portugal-moved-to-colombia-dream-home-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThen%20we%20did%20Porto%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20really%20cool%2C%20and%20then%20we%20ended%20in%20Lisbon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20slefie%20of%20a%20man%20and%20woman%20in%20Lisbon.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e9262aa98bc8fdc096d97a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBiss%20and%20his%20girlfriend%20in%20Lisbon.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Zachary%20Biss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20in%2C%20we%20paid%20%242%2C500%20total%2C%20so%20definitely%20more%20than%20two%20flights%2C%20but%20I%20would%20say%20it%20was%20worth%20the%20cost.%20The%20transatlantics%20are%20usually%20a%20bargain%20because%20they're%20not%20that%20full%20and%20they're%20just%20trying%20to%20sell%20tickets%20to%20make%20the%20voyage%20worth%20it%20%E2%80%94%20we%20actually%20got%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcomparison-balcony-rooms-cruises-royal-caribbean-utopia-virgin-voyages-valiant-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20balcony%20room%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20biggest%20perk%20was%20that%20there%20was%20no%20hard%20luggage%20limit.%20I%20brought%20my%20guitar%2C%20I%20brought%20my%20suitcases%2C%20Marina%20brought%20a%20bunch%20of%20her%20suitcases%20%E2%80%94%20as%20much%20as%20we%20could%20fit%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we%20got%20to%20the%20port%20and%20the%20porter's%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20many%20luggage%20tags%20do%20you%20need%3F%26quot%3B%20And%20we%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHowever%20many.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlying%20would%20have%20been%20a%20lot%20more%20restrictive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20thought%20that%20sailing%20would%20ease%20us%20into%20moving%20a%20little%20more%20than%20flying%20would%2C%20because%20there's%20really%20nothing%20worse%20than%20landing%20at%20Lisbon%20Airport%20after%20an%20overnight%20flight%2C%20not%20sleeping%20on%20the%20plane%2C%20and%20dealing%20with%20that%20brutal%20jet%20lag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20cruise%2C%20there%20were%20six%20days%20at%20sea%20in%20a%20row%2C%20and%20they%20would%20roll%20forward%20the%20clock%20one%20hour%20at%20a%20time%3B%20they%20did%20that%20five%20times%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20trip%20to%20get%20us%20five%20hours%20ahead%20to%20where%20we%20are%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20totally%20recommend%20moving%20by%20boat%20for%20the%20luggage%20benefit%20alone%2C%20but%20especially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froyal-caribbean-solo-cruise-surprises%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eif%20you're%20a%20cruiser%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20you%20just%20like%20relaxing%2C%20it's%20like%20being%20at%20the%20spa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20fun%2C%20and%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20many%20people%20get%20to%20say%20they've%20sailed%20across%20the%20ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220615b018-ec18-4644-b255-4e71206340df%5C%22%3EWe%20like%20the%20pace%20of%20life%20in%20Portugal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20night%2C%20we%20were%20sitting%20at%20the%20dinner%20table%2C%20and%20we%20looked%20at%20each%20other%2C%20and%20we%20both%20started%20crying%2C%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20we%20doing%3F%26quot%3B%20But%20I%20think%20that's%20100%25%20normal%20for%20anyone%20moving%2C%20even%20just%20moving%20to%20another%20state.%20It's%20scary.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20I've%20moved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20things%20pushing%20us%20out%20of%20the%20US%20and%20things%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-2-kids-moved-nyc-to-portugal-right-choice-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebringing%20us%20to%20Portugal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Honestly%2C%20the%20biggest%20one%20was%20health%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20self-employed%20person%20in%20the%20States%2C%20I%20often%20feel%20punished%20for%20being%20self-employed%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20health%20insurance.%20The%20cheapest%20plan%20offered%20to%20me%20on%20the%20marketplace%20for%20this%20year%20was%20about%20%24360%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20and%20woman%20at%20the%20Arco%20da%20Rua%20Augusta%20in%20Portugal.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e926293fecbb42897a2d41%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBiss%20and%20his%20girlfriend%20at%20the%20Arco%20da%20Rua%20Augusta%20in%20Portugal.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Zachary%20Biss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20talk%20to%20my%20friends%20who%20live%20here%20or%20have%20moved%20here%2C%20and%20I%20tell%20them%20what%20I%20paid%20in%20a%20month%2C%20they're%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20that's%20about%20what%20I%20pay%20in%20a%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAffordability%20wasn't%20the%20only%20reason%20we%20moved.%20If%20we%20were%20going%20for%20affordability%2C%20there%20are%20definitely%20cheaper%20places%20in%20Portugal%2C%20and%20even%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-affordable-cities-travel-europe-2017-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eaffordable%20places%20in%20Europe%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20all%20relative%3B%20what's%20affordable%20to%20me%20might%20be%20different%20than%20what's%20affordable%20to%20a%20local%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20people%2C%20in%20broad%20strokes%2C%20are%20in%20a%20little%20bit%20less%20of%20a%20rush%20here.%20I%20made%20a%20joke%20that%20even%20the%20people%20trying%20to%20sell%20you%20something%20off%20the%20street%2C%20once%20they%20realize%20you're%20not%20going%20to%20buy%20what%20they're%20selling%2C%20they'll%20just%20have%20a%20conversation%20with%20you%2C%20which%20is%20nice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20selfie%20of%20a%20man%20and%20woman%20holding%20an%20ice-cream%20cone.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e92629a98bc8fdc096d979%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBiss%20enjoying%20ice%20cream%20in%20Portugal.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Zachary%20Biss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pace%20of%20life%20is%20not%20so%20much%20work%2C%20work%2C%20work%20all%20the%20time%2C%20rush%2C%20rush%2C%20rush.%20People%20here%20really%20will%20take%20a%20moment%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20built%20into%20the%20day%20to%20have%20a%20coffee%2C%20have%20your%20pastry%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20and%20you're%20not%20just%20grabbing%20your%20big%20iced%20coffee%20and%20getting%20in%20your%20car%20and%20rushing%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20breath%20of%20fresh%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-florida-to-portugal-via-transatlantic-cruise-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777211701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e92ffc367066d7c296fcf9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-florida-to-portugal-via-transatlantic-cruise-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rising%20living%20costs%20in%20the%20US%20drove%20Zachary%20Biss%20to%20move%20to%20Lisbon%2C%20Portugal.%20He%20took%20a%20transatlantic%20cruise%20to%20move%20there%20and%20enjoyed%20the%20benefits.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpandy%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Pandy)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Himanta%20wife%20passport%20row%3A%20Khera%20moves%20SC%20for%20anticipatory%20bail%20after%20setback%20from%20HC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777211496000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-130533179%2Cimgsize-73408.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fhimanta-wife-passport-row-pawan-khera-moves-sc-for-anticipatory-bail-after-setback-from-guwahati-hc%2Farticleshow%2F130533108.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Gauhati%20high%20court%20had%20on%20April%2024%20rejected%20Khera's%20plea%20for%20anticipatory%20bail%20in%20the%20case%20registered%20against%20him%20by%20the%20Crime%20Branch%20of%20Assam%20Police%20in%20Guwahati.%20The%20case%20against%20Khera%20was%20registered%20after%20he%20claimed%20at%20a%20press%20brief%20that%20%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8BAssam%20CM's%20wife%20