writers%2C%20and%20Dan%20%5BErickson%5D%2C%20all%20the%20time.%20I%20know%20everything%20about%20what%E2%80%99s%20going%20on.%20%5BAs%20an%20actor%5D%20I%20like%20having%20as%20much%20information%20as%20possible.%E2%80%9D%20Just%20like%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Marta%20Balaga%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Our%20colleague%20was%20in%20the%20room%20when%20chaos%20erupted%20at%20DC's%20annual%20press%20dinner.%20Here's%20what%20he%20thought%20about%20the%20security.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224928%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22White%20House%20Deputy%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20Dan%20Scavino%20jumps%20over%20a%20chair%20during%20the%20incident%20at%20the%20White%20House%20correspondents'%20dinner.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ee0f87367066d7c29711dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223288%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhite%20House%20Deputy%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20Dan%20Scavino%20jumps%20over%20a%20chair%20during%20the%20shooting%20incident%20at%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner.%3Cp%3EChip%20Somodevilla%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESenior%20Editor%20Tim%20R%C3%B6hn%20was%20among%20the%20attendees%20at%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20described%20the%20fear%20and%20panic%20in%20the%20room%20after%20hearing%20someone%20shout%2C%20%26quot%3BShots%20fired.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20was%20struck%20by%20how%20%26quot%3Blax%26quot%3B%20security%20was%20at%20the%20event%20throughout%20the%20evening.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20after%208%3A30%20p.m.%20on%20a%20Saturday%20night%2C%20chaos%20erupts%20in%20the%20ballroom%20of%20the%20Hilton%20Hotel%20in%20Washington%2C%20and%20a%20wave%20of%20fear%20sweeps%20through%20the%20room.%20I%20am%20seated%20at%20one%20of%20roughly%20200%20tables%20when%20I%20suddenly%20hear%20dull%2C%20thudding%20sounds%20cutting%20through%20the%20loud%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarely%20a%20second%20later%2C%20people%20begin%20throwing%20themselves%20to%20the%20floor%20%E2%80%94%20first%20in%20the%20center%20of%20the%20room%2C%20near%20the%20stage%2C%20then%20everywhere.%20I%20hear%20someone%20shout%20something%20like%20%26quot%3BShooting%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BShots%20fired.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20drop%20down%20as%20well%2C%20crouching%2C%20my%20eyes%20fixed%20on%20the%20stage.%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20had%20arrived%20only%20minutes%20earlier%2C%20is%20rushed%20away.%20From%20behind%20the%20curtain%2C%20heavily%20armed%20officers%20emerge%2C%20pointing%20their%20weapons%20toward%20the%20crowd.%20Secret%20Service%20agents%20sprint%20through%20the%20ballroom%2C%20vaulting%20over%20tables%20and%20chairs.%20Glass%20shatters.%20High-ranking%20politicians%20are%20pulled%20to%20safety%20and%20ushered%20out%20of%20the%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20feels%20like%20a%20movie%20%E2%80%94%20but%20this%20is%20not%20Hollywood.%20This%20is%20reality%3A%20the%20storied%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-evacuated-from-white-house-correspondents-dinner-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWhite%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20Trump%20attending%20as%20president%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20suddenly%20transformed%20into%20the%20scene%20of%20a%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWas%20Trump%20the%20target%3F%20It%20wouldn't%20be%20the%20first%20time.%20The%20thought%20flashes%20through%20my%20mind%20in%20those%20seconds.%20I%20think%20about%20gun%20violence%20in%20the%20United%20States%20(I%20moved%20here%20only%208%20months%20ago).%20Shootings%20happen%20constantly%2C%20everywhere%20%E2%80%94%20so%20why%20not%20here%2C%20at%20the%20Trump%20dinner%3F%20I%20am%20shaken%2C%20but%20not%20surprised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20all-clear%20is%20given%2C%20yet%20after%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20people%20slowly%20get%20back%20on%20their%20feet.%20Somehow%2C%20things%20must%20go%20on.%20Phones%20come%20out%3B%20people%20film%2C%20text%2C%20try%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20what%20just%20happened.%20It%20remains%20completely%20unclear%20what%20occurred%20%E2%80%94%20only%20one%20thing%20is%20certain%3A%20no%20one%20is%20allowed%20to%20leave%20the%20ballroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20word%20spreads%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcole-allen-shooter-white-house-correspondents-dinner-trump-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20%26quot%3Bshooter%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20apprehended%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20lobby%2C%20I%20feel%20a%20sense%20of%20relief.%20Twice%2C%20an%20announcement%20follows%20that%20the%20event%20will%20resume%20shortly.%20But%20it%20never%20does.%20Trump%20himself%20invites%20the%20press%20to%20the%20White%20House%20for%20a%20briefing%3B%20the%20dinner%20is%20over.%20Guests%20are%20asked%20to%20leave%20the%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20way%20out%2C%20I%20think%20about%20the%20security%20precautions%20%E2%80%94%20or%20lack%20thereof%20%E2%80%94%20that%20had%20struck%20me%20as%20surprisingly%20lax%20throughout%20the%20evening%2C%20given%20the%20presence%20of%20Trump%2C%20Vice%20President%20JD%20Vance%2C%20and%20several%20cabinet%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20hours%20before%2C%20traffic%20outside%20the%20Hilton%20had%20ground%20to%20a%20halt%2C%20and%20I%20had%20jumped%20out%20of%20my%20taxi%20about%20500%20meters%20away%20and%20walked%20the%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20outside%20the%20hotel%2C%20there%20are%20shouting%20Trump%20opponents%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20harassed%20and%20insulted%20dinner%20guests.%20All%20it%20took%20to%20gain%20access%20to%20the%20premises%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20hotel%20%E2%80%94%20was%20flashing%20a%20screenshot%20of%20an%20invitation%20while%20passing%20by.%20Only%20those%20heading%20into%20the%20ballroom%20on%20a%20lower%20level%20had%20to%20pass%20through%20a%20metal%20detector.%20No%20need%20to%20remove%20a%20jacket.%20No%20request%20for%20a%20passport%20or%20ID.%20Once%2C%20even%20activists%20managed%20to%20slip%20onto%20the%20red%20carpet%20to%20protest%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIs%20that%20adequate%20security%20for%20such%20a%20high-profile%20event%3F%20I%20wouldn't%20presume%20to%20deliver%20a%20final%20judgment%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20am%20certain%20of%20one%20thing%3A%20it%20will%20be%20debated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETim%20R%C3%B6hn%20is%20a%20senior%20editor%20at%20Business%20Insider's%20parent%20company%2C%20Axel%20Springer.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhitlon-hotel-washington-shooting-witness-white-house-correspondents-dinner-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777210593000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ee0fab367066d7c29711de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhitlon-hotel-washington-shooting-witness-white-house-correspondents-dinner-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Business%20Insider%20had%20a%20colleague%20as%20a%20guest%20at%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner.%20This%20is%20his%20witness%20account.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Insider%20Inc.)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Giddens%20Ko%20and%20Kai%20Ko%20Bring%20%E2%80%98Kung%20Fu%E2%80%99%20to%20Far%20East%20Film%20Fest%2C%20Reveal%20Stephen%20Chow%20Input%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777210349000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236730800%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Taiwanese%20filmmaker%20Giddens%20Ko%2C%20presenting%20%E2%80%9CKung%20Fu%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20Far%20East%20Film%20Festival%20on%20Saturday%2C%20revealed%20that%20Stephen%20Chow%20contributed%20to%20the%20film%E2