tin%2C%20Texas%2C%20for%20a%20short-term%20internship%20in%20my%20mid-20s%2C%20I%20never%20intended%20to%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20new%20graduate%2C%20my%20goal%20was%20to%20get%20some%20hands-on%20experience%20in%20international%20business%20practices%20before%20returning%20home%20to%20work%20with%20my%20dad%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteach-yoga-exchange-for-free-stays-all-inclusive-resorts-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eteach%20fitness%20classes%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20met%20the%20man%20who%20would%20become%20my%20husband.%20We%20crossed%20paths%20in%20downtown%20Austin%2C%20both%20waiting%20for%20a%20taxi%20after%20a%20night%20out.%20We%20started%20talking%2C%20felt%20an%20instant%20connection%2C%20and%20from%20that%20night%20on%2C%20kept%20finding%20reasons%20to%20see%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20internship%20ended%2C%20I%20returned%20to%20Poland%20as%20planned.%20A%20long-distance%20relationship%20wasn't%20easy%2C%20but%20we%20made%20it%20work.%20One%20month%20after%20I%20left%2C%20he%20flew%20to%20Poland%2C%20proposed%2C%20and%20suddenly%2C%20the%20life%20I%20thought%20I%20was%20building%20there%20no%20longer%20felt%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e966947e-6352-4831-9486-f1a99e9d0d46%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20left%20behind%20a%20clear-cut%20path%20and%20rebuilt%20my%20life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22904%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20writer%20and%20her%20husband%20sitting%20on%20a%20bench%20in%20front%20of%20the%20water.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e2624d367066d7c296e00c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22706%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOver%20time%2C%20I%20built%20a%20life%20I%20love%20in%20the%20US.%3Cp%3EKarol%20Dugan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20moved%20back%20to%20the%20US%20and%20we%20got%20married%2C%20I%20left%20behind%20more%20than%20my%20country.%20I%20walked%20away%20from%20a%20defined%20career%20path%2C%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworked-at-my-mothers-business-alongside-sister-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efamily%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20comfort%20of%20knowing%20exactly%20where%20I%20belonged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarting%20over%20as%20an%20immigrant%20was%20harder%20than%20I%20expected.%20As%20soon%20as%20I%20got%20my%20work%20permit%2C%20I%20took%20the%20first%20job%20offer%20I%20got.%20I%20felt%20pressure%20to%20prove%20%E2%80%94%20to%20my%20family%2C%20my%20friends%2C%20and%20myself%20%E2%80%94%20that%20I%20was%20succeeding%20in%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20a%20job%20quickly%20felt%20like%20validation.%20In%20hindsight%2C%20it%20was%20a%20mistake.%20The%20role%20wasn't%20right%2C%20but%20I%20stayed%20longer%20than%20I%20should%20have.%20As%20a%20new%20immigrant%2C%20I%20didn't%20think%20I%20could%20afford%20to%20be%20selective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20became%20pregnant%20with%20my%20first%20child%2C%20I%20quit%20my%20job%20and%20made%20a%20difficult%20but%20necessary%20decision%3A%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmother-enrolled-college-midlife-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewent%20back%20to%20college%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20earned%20a%20degree%20in%20computer%20information%20technology%20and%20eventually%20started%20a%20new%20career%20in%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20since%20moving%20to%20the%20US%2C%20I%20felt%20stable%20again.%20I%20had%20rebuilt%20my%20confidence%20and%20proven%20to%20myself%20that%20starting%20over%20didn't%20mean%20starting%20from%20nothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20something%20was%20missing.%20In%20Poland%2C%20I%20had%20always%20envisioned%20myself%20running%20a%20business.%20That%20dream%20never%20disappeared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlongside%20my%20tech%20career%2C%20I%20started%20my%20own%20fitness%20coaching%20business.%20Through%20it%2C%20I%20met%20inspiring%20women%20in%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20entrepreneurs%2C%20mothers%2C%20immigrants%20%E2%80%94%20who%20helped%20me%20rediscover%20my%20ambition%20and%20sense%20of%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20nearly%2010%20years%2C%20but%20slowly%2C%20the%20US%20started%20feeling%20like%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22478881d2-7670-4bb8-a02e-55024171be9b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhile%20I%20was%20building%20a%20home%20in%20Austin%2C%20my%20husband%20was%20falling%20in%20love%20with%20Poland%20%E2%80%94%20but%20we've%20found%20a%20compromise%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22886%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20writer%20hugging%20her%20husband%20in%20front%20of%20a%20wood%20house.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e262773fecbb42897a1161%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22694%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20decided%20to%20consider%20buying%20property%20in%20Poland.%3Cp%3EKarol%20Dugan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20I%20felt%20rooted%2C%20my%20husband%20started%20dreaming%20of%20the%20life%20I%20once%20left%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20our%20marriage%2C%20we%20traveled%20back%20to%20Poland%20often.%20Over%20time%2C%20my%20husband%20fell%20for%20the%20things%20I%20once%20took%20for%20granted%3A%20the%20slower%20pace%20of%20life%2C%20the%20food%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-walkable-cities-for-pedestrians-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewalkable%20cities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20mountain%20views%20near%20my%20hometown%2C%20and%20the%20old%20architecture%20layered%20with%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20his%20curiosity%20turned%20more%20serious.%20He%20began%20talking%20about%20what%20daily%20life%20there%20might%20look%20like%2C%20bringing%20up%20how%20it%20would%20feel%20to%20enjoy%20slower%20mornings%20and%20spend%20more%20time%20with%20my%20family.%20After%20one%20memorable%20visit%20last%20year%2C%20he%20asked%20if%20I'd%20be%20open%20to%20planning%20a%20future%20in%20Poland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20no%20longer%20felt%20abstract.%20I%20agreed%20to%20start%20looking%20at%20property%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20a%20piece%20of%20land%2C%20or%20even%20a%20small%20house%20%E2%80%94%20sometime%20in%20the%20next%20year%20or%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20conversations.%20We%20discussed%20our%20careers%2C%20finances%2C%20children%2C%20and%20what%20we%20wanted%20our%20future%20to%20look%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20we%20compromised%3A%20We'll%20stay%20in%20the%20US%20for%20the%20time%20being%2C%20but%20buy%20property%20in%20Poland%20within%20the%20next%20year%20or%20two.%20We'll%20visit%20as%20much%20as%20we%20can%20and%20plan%20to%20eventually%20retire%20there%2C%20about%20three%20decades%20from%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-moved-to-mexico-for-love-mistake-broke-up-left-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMoving%20countries%20for%20love%3C%2Fa%3E%20taught%20me%20that%20rebuilding%20takes%20time%2C%20and%20clarity%20doesn't%20come%20all%20at%20once.%20It%20also%20taught%20me%20that%20home%20isn't%20%3Cem%3Ejust%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%20geography%2C%20but%20choosing%20each%20other%2C%20no%20matter%20where%20you%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-for-love-to-us-from-poland-adjustment-new-career-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777209181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e2646ba98bc8fdc096bdcb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-for-love-to-us-from-poland-adjustment-new-career-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20moving%20from%20Poland%20to%20the%20US%20for%20love%2C%20it%20took%20some%20time%20to%20adjust%20to%20life%20here.%20Now%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20are%20discussing%20moving%20to%20Poland.%22%